articles.title: More injury woe for South Africa with experienced pair out of Australia clash - ICC Cricket
articles.description: South Africa's injury woes continue to mount up ahead of the ICC Men's Cricket World Cup with a pair of experienced players ruled out of the fourth ODI against Australia at Centurion.
